Moco-chan, do you have a favorite part?

00:06:24.219 --> 00:06:26.275
- I like the beginning too.
- The beginning?

00:06:26.881 --> 00:06:29.772
There's a part in the very very
beginning, Moco-chan, that you sing,

00:06:29.796 --> 00:06:32.686
that your voice gets all like...

00:06:32.706 --> 00:06:34.771
- I like that part.
- What part is that?

00:06:35.093 --> 00:06:36.998
<i>Subarashiki sekai e...</i>

00:06:39.125 --> 00:06:40.501
I'm not too sure.

00:06:41.022 --> 00:06:43.082
You have to listen closely, Ruffians.

00:06:43.202 --> 00:06:45.323
It'll be in the first couple seconds.

00:06:45.723 --> 00:06:49.504
We've seen in the comments that a lot
of listeners seem to hear Marine-senpai.

00:06:49.544 --> 00:06:57.067
Marine-senpai... Last time I checked,
she's... She's not part of FUWAMOCO.

00:06:57.287 --> 00:06:59.747
Unfortunately, she's not.

00:06:59.807 --> 00:07:03.295
